j.

 Description of Project:

 The proposed project would consist of: (1) An existing 12-foot-high earth and rockfill dam; (2) an 18 acre reservoir
with a storage capacity of 55-acre-feet; (3) a 36-inch-diameter, 2,584-foot-long penstock; (4) a powerhouse containing
a generating unit with a capacity of 113 kW and an estimated average annual generation of 900 MWh; (5) a 50-foot-long
underground transmission line connecting to an existing Idaho Power Company distribution line; and (6) appurtenant
facilities. 


